rows.label: tlk70000019_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Do you folks ever go meet the families
of the people you've helped?

rows.label: tlk70000019_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm sure their families would want to
express their thanks to you, too.

rows.label: tlk70000019_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm a firm believer in the fact that
meeting someone and talking to them
helps deepen the bonds between you.

rows.label: tlk70000019_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It's OK for you to not go visit my
husband, though.

rows.label: tlk70000019_04_msg0005
rows.name:
There's no good'll come of you
deepening your bonds with that
blockhead! Humph!
